{"lastModified":1768912890782,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nOur new Hanse 388 “Calypso” (2022) offers a lot for a 38 foot yacht, with a large rig and sail area coupled with the long waterline, the cruising performance sets the Hanse 388 apart from the rest. A spacious cockpit ensures that there is plenty of room for relaxing when at anchor or even when under sail. Large port lights in the hull and large deck hatches mean the interior is bathed in light which compliments the space. This great sailing yacht has 3 cabins and 1 head, and it is very easy to handle. The Hanse 388 is an ideal boat for short handed sailing, with all lines led to the helmsman there is no need to leave the wheel, from slipping your lines until you return to your berth.\n\nHanse have a reputation for building strong, safe cruising yachts and the 388 continues this tradition. Under sail you can feel the strength and stiffness of the hand-built hull which will reassure you when enjoying your time out on the water.\n\nHanse 388 is ideal boat for smaller crews and families to Feel at home on the high seas.\n\nHanse 388 “Calypso” is located in Marina Baotić, Seget Donji, Croatia and is available for all bookings in season 2023!","blueprint":{"name":"CALYPSO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111::assets::20c12b80-4b76-11f0-97cb-4fc7b1896435/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111::assets::20cf3540-4b76-11f0-97cc-4fc7b1896435/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111::assets::20e2bd40-4b76-11f0-97cc-4fc7b1896435/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111::assets::21049d20-4b76-11f0-97cc-4fc7b1896435/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::80f02ed0-4b70-11f0-a2ad-d1d9e18dc111::assets::20c79420-4b76-11f0-97cc-4fc7b18964